snippet.title: FIFA 23 | Official Launch Trailer | Matchday For The World’s Game
snippet.description:
It’s Matchday. Everywhere.

Play FIFA 23 now: http://x.ea.com/74742

Featuring Kylian Mbappé, Sam Kerr, Chloe Kelly, Virgil van Dijk, Jack Grealish, Zidane, Vinícius Jr., and Heung-Min Son.

Get FIFA 23 and play FUT by October 7 to get a Historic Cover ICON on a 23-match loan: [link to historic icon web page]

See what’s new in FIFA 23, with HyperMotion2 Technology, women’s club football, both men’s and women’s FIFA World Cup™ tournaments, cross-play features, and more: https://www.ea.com/games/fifa/fifa-23/new-features-and-modes

Subscribe to see more FIFA 23 videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

#FIFA23 #TheWorldsGame
